# Telegram ChatGPT Bot

## Setup and Run

### Clone

```bash
git clone --branch master https://github.com/pourya90091/Telegram-ChatGPT-Bot.git
```

### Install Requirements

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

- Download and install ffmpeg (in any way you can).

```bash
sudo apt install ffmpeg
```

### Configuration

- Go to configs.py to configure the bot.

### Run

```bash
python bot.py
```

